cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with natural language generation from medical images, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a multi-task learning framework and a co-attention mechanism, which are common techniques in machine learning and deep learning, respectively. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it deals with finding abnormalities in medical images, and generating reports based on them. Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as well.
